import React from "react"; import "../projects/Projects.css"; import "./community.css"; import { Fade } from "react-reveal"; export default function Community() { return (

Community Engagements

Jan 2025: Career Exploration Lounge @ Re-writing The Code - Tech Connect 2025

Jan 2025: Featured @ WomenTech Network Highlights 2025

Dec 2024: PyLadies Con 2024

Oct 2024: Awarded Python Triager Open-Source @ Python Software Foundation

Sep 2024: Python Core Dev Sprints 2024

Jul 2024: Python Pyninsula Meetup 2024

Jun 2024: North Bay Python 2024

May 2024: Session Runner @ PyCon US 2024

Mar 2024: Led Meta Platforms' representation @ SCaLE 21x 2024

Sep 2023: Grace Hopper Celebration 2023

Jun 2022: 2022 New York R Conference

Jun 2021 - Apr 2022: Mentor @ Rewriting The Code

Feb 2021: Communications Lead @ Voices of Data Science, University of Massachusetts Amherst

Oct 2019: Yahoo Finance All Markets Summit 2019: Generational Opportunities

Oct 2018: PyCon India 2018

Mar 2016: Represented IIT Indore @ Festival of Innovation 2016, Department of Science and Technology, Government of India at Rastrapati Bhawan (President's House), India

Dec 2015: Represented IIT Indore @ India International Science Fair 2015, Ministry of Science and Technology, Government of India held at IIT Delhi

 ); }
